# Project Overview

This project is a full-stack To-Do List Web Application developed using Node.js, React, Docker, DockerHub, and Render.com.

The application allows users to:
- Add tasks
- Edit tasks
- Delete tasks
- Store tasks using backend APIs

The project demonstrates:
- Frontend and backend integration
- Environment variable configuration
- Docker containerization
- DockerHub image deployment
- Render.com cloud deployment
- CI/CD concepts

---

# Technologies Used

Technology  	Purpose
React (Vite)	Frontend UI
Node.js	        Backend runtime
Express.js	    REST API creation
Axios	        API communication
PostgreSQL	    Database (Render)
Docker	        Containerization
DockerHub	    Image registry
Jenkins	        CI/CD pipeline automation
Render.com	    Cloud deployment platform
GitHub	        Version control
Jest	        Unit testing
dotenv	        Environment variable management

